          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Combat Violent Crime Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill modifies the approach used to determine if a criminal offense is a crime of violence for purposes of imposing an enhanced sentence on a defendant who uses or possesses a firearm in a crime of violence.</p>]]></text>
